preibisch_imagej.types

Class BigComplex

  • java.lang.Object
    • preibisch_imagej.types.BigComplex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComplexType<BigComplex>, NumericType<BigComplex>, Add<BigComplex>, Div<BigComplex>, Mul<BigComplex>, MulFloatingPoint, SetOne, SetZero, Sub<BigComplex>, Type<BigComplex>

    public class BigComplex
extends Object
implements ComplexType<BigComplex>
    A complex number that stores values in BigDecimal (arbitrary) precision. Besides providing precise numeric operations this class is useful for supporting DataType translations with minimal data loss. Some methods may round values to 50 decimal places of precision.
    Author:
    Barry DeZonia
